5/we-want-to-grow-our-support-team/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:74:"https://www.layerswp.com/2017/05/we-want-to-grow-our-support-team/#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Wed, 24 May 2017 09:50:45 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4:"News";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:32:"http://www.layerswp.com/?p=12608";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:318:"<p>We are looking for a full time support person to work at Layers.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.layerswp.com/2017/05/we-want-to-grow-our-support-team/">We&#8217;re Hiring! We want to grow our Support Team!</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.layerswp.com">Layers</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"David Perel";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1996:"<p>Ever since Obox Themes, we&#8217;ve prided ourselves in offering the best support possible and when we launched Layers we wanted to take it to another level.</p>\n<p>We started by offering support for free to anyone who was using Layers. Things are¬†going well but as Layers has grown (over 650k downloads and¬†<em>many thousands</em> of active sites) we have¬†realised that it&#8217;s time to grow our support team again.</p>\n<p>Currently our support team consists of Vail Joy,¬†Marc and myself. However we need someone who is 100% focussed on the task of support so that we can reply to queries quicker.</p>\n<h3>What we are looking for:</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>You must be fluent in English</li>\n<li>Have an excellent understanding of WordPress and how it works</li>\n<li>Have an excellent understanding of WooCommerce and how it works</li>\n<li>Experience with Layers and it&#8217;s fundamental workings</li>\n<li>Experience in the Theme industry</li>\n<li>Ability to write¬†front end code and understand, on a basic level, backend code</li>\n<li>You can work from anywhere in the world we just require that you respond to support messages quickly and accurately. Be aware that most of our customers reside in America, so you will need to respond during their waking hours.</li>\n<li><em>Most importantly</em> you need to have a thick skin, the support game is tough and your ability to drill down to the question at hand is key</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Applicants will be put through a short test and interview process before the final decision is made. If you think you have what it takes to join the ranks at Layers¬†then please <a href="https://www.layerswp.com/contact/">contact us here</a>¬†with a short paragraph on why you think you&#8217;re the right choice.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.layerswp.com/2017/05/we-want-to-grow-our-support-team/">We&#8217;re Hiring! We want to grow our Support Team!</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.layerswp.com">Layers</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:71:"https://www.layerswp.com/2017/05/we-want-to-grow-our-support-team/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b