com/2016/10/make-rayne-latest-layers-blog-theme/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Mon, 31 Oct 2016 08:50:11 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4:"News";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"themes";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:32:"http://www.layerswp.com/?p=10024";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:380:"<p>Rayne is a beautiful Blog Theme for Layers that was originally produced by the team at Bright Levels and launched on Themeforest.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.layerswp.com/2016/10/make-rayne-latest-layers-blog-theme/">Make it Rayne with the latest Layers blog theme</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.layerswp.com">Layers</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"David Perel";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:3439:"<p>Rayne, a WordPress Blog Theme for Layers, was originally produced by¬†<a href="https://dribbble.com/Brightlevels" target="_blank">Joel Bohorquez</a> and launched on Themeforest. However we¬†noticed recently that it was no longer listed which made us sad. So we quickly got in touch with their team and acquired the theme.</p>\n<h4>Beautiful Design</h4>\n<div id="attachment_10027" style="width: 1010px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://www.layerswp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/blog-rayne-screenshots.jpg"><img class="wp-image-10027 size-full" src="https://www.layerswp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/blog-rayne-screenshots.jpg" alt="blog-rayne-screenshots" width="1000" height="600" srcset="https://www.layerswp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/blog-rayne-screenshots.jpg 1000w, https://www.layerswp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/blog-rayne-screenshots-300x180.jpg 300w, https://www.layerswp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/blog-rayne-screenshots-768x461.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Make your blog beautiful with Rayne</p></div>\n<p>What immediately attracted us to Rayne was the beautiful design of a single post page. We love the large post header and well structured typography.</p>\n<p>Not only that but the social media share buttons at the <a href="http://sites.layerswp.com/rayne/2016/02/08/when-he-could-eat-no-more-the-old-man-sighed/">bottom of each post</a> are a welcome addition that we hope to soon integrate in all Layers themes!</p>\n<h4>New Instagram Widget</h4>\n<div id="attachment_10028" style="width: 1010px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://www.layerswp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/blog-rayne-instagram.jpg"><img class="wp-image-10028 size-full" src="https://www.layerswp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/blog-rayne-instagram.jpg" alt="blog-rayne-instagram" width="1000" height="600" srcset="https://www.layerswp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/blog-rayne-instagram.jpg 1000w, https://www.layerswp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/blog-rayne-instagram-300x180.jpg 300w, https://www.layerswp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/blog-rayne-instagram-768x461.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Include an Instagram feed to the bottom of your site with a just a few clicks.</p></div>\n<p>A pattern that&#8217;s emerging with our recent themes is at least one¬†feature that&#8217;s unique to that template. Rayne is no different¬†as we launch a new¬†Instagram widget that is without doubt the easiest thing on the planet to use.</p>\n<p>All you got to do is enter in your username and Layers will automatically output a feed of your latest photos in the footer of your site. Oh and it also works in the regular¬†blog / page sidebar area.</p>\n<p>We are hoping to build this widget into Layers Pro in the near future, so stay tuned on that.</p>\n<h3>Demo and Purchase</h3>\n<p>You can take a look at the <a href="http://sites.layerswp.com/rayne/">Rayne demo here</a> or head over to the¬†Layers marketplace and <a href="https://www.layerswp.com/product/rayne-blog-theme/">purchase Rayne</a> right away. As always we have a¬†$10 discount launch special!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.layerswp.com/2016/10/make-rayne-latest-layers-blog-theme/">Make it Rayne with the latest Layers blog theme</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.layerswp.com">Layers</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:74:"https://www.layerswp.com/2016/10/make-rayne-latest-layers-blog-theme/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"5";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:48:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:58:"Ink Drop, a portfolio theme brought back by popular demand";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s: